WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.000
narrator: a portal is booted on loopback to resolve oct:// URLs.

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:09.000
narrator: /healthz responds, confirming the resolver is live.

00:00:09.000 --> 00:00:16.000
narrator: fetching an oct:// asset prints its bytes to stdout.

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:23.000
narrator: same asset, saved to disk with the served Content-Type.

00:00:23.000 --> 00:00:27.000
narrator: the policy file is plain JSON, served from the chain.

00:00:27.000 --> 00:00:35.000
narrator: an interactive fetch will prompt before opening sealed assets.
